**Story**

Once upon a time in a forest , there lived monkey who resided on a berry tree, which was on the barks of a river.It the same forest ,there lived a Crocodile and his wife.....
One day the crocodile came into the banks of the riverand rested under the tree. Thee monkey offeref him some fruits.The crocodile came back the next day for more fruits as he love them . As these path files the monkey became good friends 